Comment: Review Article. 90 pages, 14 figures. Contents: Introduction;
  Communicability in Networks; Physical Analogies; Comparing Communicability
  Functions; Communicability and the Analysis of Networks; Communicability and
  Localization in Complex Networks; Computability of Communicability Functions;
  Conclusions and Prespectives

Comment: 16 pages, 19 figures, 1 table; accepted by the Astrophysical journal;
  figure 13 is updated; electronic only movie can be found from
  http://www.astro.purdue.edu/MOJAVE/bllacpaper2.mpg
